`rank t ≤ rank h'` by metis_tac [] >-
decide_tac >-
(fs [EVERY_MEM] >>
 metis_tac [arithmeticTheory.LESS_LESS_EQ_TRANS]) >>
`rank t = rank h'` by decide_tac >>
